 height="110" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://emptynestthemes.com/2012/09/03/autumn-leaf-wordpress-theme/"><strong>Autumn Leaf</strong></a> is a rich, textured theme with a leaf background.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-11911" title="commodore" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/commodore.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/commodore"><strong>Commodore</strong></a> is an HTML5 and CSS3 theme in the style of the good old Commodore 64.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-11912" title="priimo" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/priimo.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/priimo"><strong>Priimo</strong></a> is a lightweight, clean, and elegant theme.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-11910" title="seismicslate" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/seismicslate.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/seismic-slate"><strong>Seismic Slate</strong></a> is an excellent minimal theme, with a &#8220;hiding&#8221; menu on scroll.</p>\n<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-11914" title="shiro" src="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/shiro.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="113" /></p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/shiro"><strong>Shiro</strong></a> is a clean and minimal three-column CMS and blog theme.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/Rm2ePalQ3hc" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 05 Sep 2012 14:30:06 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a