age configuration files where it was necessary and implemented solutions to issues we found. Most important, we are in direct contact with the authors to resolve any issues that may come up on our Support forum. We hope you enjoy this issue of our bulletin.</p>\n<div id="masonry">\n<div class="feature"><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/building-blocks"><img class="size-full wp-image-74230 alignleft" title="building-blocks" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/building-blocks.png" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\n<h2>Building Blocks &#8211; Boilerplate Theme</h2>\n<p>A theme skeleton that has everything you need to quickly start building feature-rich themes without the bloat of theme frameworks.</p>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/building-blocks" target="_blank">Download Boilerplate</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/daisho-flexible-wordpress-portfolio-theme/2585124" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-74255" title="daisho-theme" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/daisho-theme.png" alt="" width="300" /></a></p>\n<h2>Daisho &#8211; Flexible WordPress Portfolio Theme</h2>\n<p>Daisho is a portfolio solution for creative professionals and companies looking for a minimal and professional look. Flexible and responsive presentation, smooth navigational flow and clutter-free approach. Put your works in focus. Powerful Typography Plugin included.</p>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/daisho-flexible-wordpress-portfolio-theme/2585124" target="_blank">Purchase Daisho</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/infringe-responsive-business-corporate-wp/2899826" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-74268" title="infringe-theme" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/