e worked together with them to make sure everything works perfectly when used in conjunction with WPML. Pinword is a fantastic looking blog theme that is also very feature rich and customizable and available in three different colors. This theme provides all the main functionality you will need to present your products, work and yourself in an elegant and professional style.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/pinword-personal-and-blog-wordpress-theme/2419260" target="_blank">Purchase Pinword</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Responsive &#8211; Free Responsive WordPress Theme</h2>\n<p><img class="size-full wp-image-68302 aligncenter" title="responsive-preview" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/responsive-preview.jpg" alt="" width="590" height="591" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>Make <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/responsive">responsive</a> part of your starting Theme design, or upgrade your current one to a mobile friendly Theme that automatically adapts to any* screen resolution or device. Responsive WordPress Theme that features 9 page Templates. There is also full width page, sitemap Template as well as landing page for your PPC or any other purposes. Responsive also supports 9 widget areas and best of all this Theme is crafted with fluid proportion-based grid system of their own to adapt the design to the viewing environment. There are also Theme Options to control the content, webmaster tools, logo managament, social icons and 4 navigation menus. Currently translated in 22 languages.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/responsive" target="_blank">Download Responsive</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>We are working on themes and plugins for our next compatibility bulletin. Check out the <a class="vt-p" title="Go-Global program" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatib